               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>An incomplete <title xml:lang="ta">Tivākaram</title>:  chapter 1 only, that is, the <foreign xml:lang="ta">Teyvappeyarttokuti</foreign> ("section on the names of gods").</p>
<p>By a Christian copiyst (see Christian crosses, Christian blessing, and Christian invocation, that is, a Christianized version of the traditional invocation of the <title xml:lang="ta">Tivākaram</title>).</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (November 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
